"{\"uid\": \"independent.co.uk-sport-olympics-keely-hodgkinson-paris-olympics-team-gb-b2583605.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Notifications can be managed in browser preferences.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 52, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in  Swipe for next article  Hodgkinson is the favourite for gold in the women's 800m having won silver in Tokyo  Removed from bookmarks  I would like to be emailed about offers, events and updates from The Independent.\", \"from\": 54, \"to\": 406, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 216, \"end\": 226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9394314193409067, \"rank\": 0.06447365865379448, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}, {\"begin\": 294, \"end\": 299, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7806867431023279, \"rank\": 0.2805156543688761, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy notice  Keely Hodgkinsonknows that she will neverexperience the lack of pressureshe enjoyed at her maidenOlympicsbut is embracing the tag of favourite at Paris 2024 this summer.\", \"from\": 407, \"to\": 600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 577, \"end\": 587, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8968794109002464e-15, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The middle-distance\\u00a0star announced herselfto the world in Tokyo three years ago, taking silver over 800m and breaking Dame Kelly Holmes' British record while still just a teenager.\", \"from\": 602, \"to\": 782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 660, \"end\": 665, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7806867431023279, \"rank\": 0.2805156543688761, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 720, \"end\": 737, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dame Kelly Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\"}, {\"begin\": 739, \"end\": 753, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"score\": 0.9999999302804123, \"rank\": 6.971004103373057e-08, \"text\": \"British record\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Progression_of_the_British_football_transfer_fee_record\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although it was not a total shock, Hodgkinson admits that in 2024 shefinds herself in a very different situation, having followed up that with two more silvers on the world stage in each of the last two summers.\", \"from\": 784, \"to\": 995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 819, \"end\": 829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9394314193409067, \"rank\": 0.06447365865379448, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throw inthe sixth-fastest women's 800m time in historyat the London Diamond League meet just before the Olympics and the expectations are suddenly stratospheric.\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1157, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1057, \"end\": 1063, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9998691996528982, \"rank\": 0.00011914885183162816, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}, {\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1078, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Diamond_League\", \"score\": 0.9997089490291002, \"rank\": 0.0002911357060525055, \"text\": \"Diamond League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Diamond_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2021_Diamond_League\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hodgkinson said: \\\"I feel like this is going to be my proper Olympic experience.\", \"from\": 1159, \"to\": 1238, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1159, \"end\": 1169, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9394314193409067, \"rank\": 0.06447365865379448, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last time with Covid, they did an amazing job putting it on.\", \"from\": 1239, \"to\": 1299, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But now, with the crowd, I think it's going to be a proper experience, so I am really excited.\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1394, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It really did change my life.\", \"from\": 1396, \"to\": 1426, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics is something that resonates with the majority of the public, so it's just really special to perform well there.\", \"from\": 1427, \"to\": 1551, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a different pressure this time.\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1590, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was very upcoming, that position I was in, I will never have that again.\", \"from\": 1591, \"to\": 1665, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The freedom of being there for the experience and it did not really matter what I did.\", \"from\": 1666, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I knew what I could do.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Now, we are three years later, I think I am a better athlete than I was then but now there is that expectation.\", \"from\": 1778, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have medalled every year now so it's a case of can we do it again?\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Can we go one better?\\\"\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 1982, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her cause has been helped by Tokyo gold medallist and 2022 world champion Athing Mu, who is three months younger than Hodgkinson,missing out at the US Olympic trials.\", \"from\": 1984, \"to\": 2150, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2013, \"end\": 2018, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7806867431023279, \"rank\": 0.2805156543688761, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 2058, \"end\": 2067, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athing_Mu\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Athing Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athing_Mu\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athing_Mu\"}, {\"begin\": 2102, \"end\": 2112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9394314193409067, \"rank\": 0.06447365865379448, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}, {\"begin\": 2132, \"end\": 2134, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9435478550155949, \"rank\": 0.0593746259695423, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Where Hodgkinson was able to skip the 800m at the UK Championships, having already clinched a place in Paris, the Americans have a cutthroat selection policy where only the top three at their trials can go to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2374, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2158, \"end\": 2168, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9394314193409067, \"rank\": 0.06447365865379448, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}, {\"begin\": 2255, \"end\": 2260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995143298, \"rank\": 4.857261408834328e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So when Mu was clipped and fell during the race, her Olympic hopes evaporated.\", \"from\": 2376, \"to\": 2454, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2384, \"end\": 2386, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"score\": 0.999798998890498, \"rank\": 0.0002010415109015266, \"text\": \"Mu\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Minnesota\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rather than count her blessings, Hodgkinson is disappointed to miss out on the chance to take on her rival, while also admitting that suffering a similar fate is something of a preoccupation.\", \"from\": 2455, \"to\": 2646, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2488, \"end\": 2498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9394314193409067, \"rank\": 0.06447365865379448, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"Unfortunately Athing is not going to be in Paris this year.\", \"from\": 2648, \"to\": 2718, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2702, \"end\": 2707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999995143298, \"rank\": 4.857261408834328e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was very gutted about that.\", \"from\": 2719, \"to\": 2748, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If it was me, I'd be devastated, it's not nice to see that happen.\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2815, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even though she's not there, it's still so hard to achieve, it's just one less person to worry about.\", \"from\": 2816, \"to\": 2917, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's going to be difficult but it's the Olympic Games, anything can happen.\", \"from\": 2918, \"to\": 2993, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"With races like that, I have had my heels clipped a few times.\", \"from\": 2995, \"to\": 3058, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It makes you wary that just because you are the best, that does not mean that it can not happen to you.\", \"from\": 3059, \"to\": 3162, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It was very unfortunate, so you just have to keep your wits about you.\", \"from\": 3163, \"to\": 3233, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"800m and 1500m are two of the messy races for that, people getting on top of each other, piling up, so you just have to stay out of trouble.\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3374, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes you can not control it, so you just have to hope the luck is on your side.\", \"from\": 3375, \"to\": 3459, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It does cross your mind sometimes, what if I fall over?\", \"from\": 3460, \"to\": 3515, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But hopefully not!\\\"\", \"from\": 3516, \"to\": 3535, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In many ways, it appears that Hodgkinson's progress has been almost all highs, settling for the odd silver medal rather than gold, notwithstanding.\", \"from\": 3537, \"to\": 3684, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3567, \"end\": 3577, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9394314193409067, \"rank\": 0.06447365865379448, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the 22-year-old admits that the aftermath of her Olympic debut was not easy and took a while to come to terms with.\", \"from\": 3685, \"to\": 3804, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She added: \\\"I have shown how mentally strong I can be.\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3860, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After Tokyo, the Olympic comedown is a real thing.\", \"from\": 3861, \"to\": 3911, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3867, \"end\": 3872, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7806867431023279, \"rank\": 0.2805156543688761, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was quite tough, being so young and having so many aspects of my life change.\", \"from\": 3912, \"to\": 3994, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did not go to university anymore, I went full-time pro.\", \"from\": 3995, \"to\": 4052, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I moved out, got my own place, all these changes you go through anyway.\", \"from\": 4053, \"to\": 4124, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And then you think I have got to do what I did last year again, for a whole year, finding that motivation.\", \"from\": 4126, \"to\": 4233, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I now know this time around that I will be better equipped to handle that.\", \"from\": 4234, \"to\": 4308, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I also want to enjoy it, I am back to really enjoying it again.\", \"from\": 4309, \"to\": 4372, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I get to that final and give it my all, I will be happy.\", \"from\": 4373, \"to\": 4432, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"After Tokyo, there was no pressure on me.\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4476, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4441, \"end\": 4446, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.7806867431023279, \"rank\": 0.2805156543688761, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only thing I did not want was to be a one-hit wonder, who just got it right then.\", \"from\": 4477, \"to\": 4562, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I wanted to prove not just to myself but to everyone else that I could be a multiple medallist.\", \"from\": 4563, \"to\": 4658, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here we are, three years later, with a lot more medals so it's good fun!\\\"\", \"from\": 4659, \"to\": 4732, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The pressure might have changed but Hodgkinson's potential remains sky-high.\", \"from\": 4734, \"to\": 4810, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4770, \"end\": 4780, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"score\": 0.9394314193409067, \"rank\": 0.06447365865379448, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hodgkinson_Minerals_Area\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now she has a gold medal to go and get.\", \"from\": 4811, \"to\": 4850, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"::National Lottery players raise more than \\u00a330million a week for good causes including vital funding into sport - from grassroots to elite.\", \"from\": 4852, \"to\": 4991, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4854, \"end\": 4870, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotteries_in_the_United_States\", \"score\": 0.591519928696561, \"rank\": 0.6905600935421985, \"text\": \"National Lottery\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotteries_in_the_United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lotteries_in_the_United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To find out more visit:www.lotterygoodcauses.org.uk#TNLAthletes  Join thought-provoking conversations, follow other Independent readers and see their replies  Please refresh the page or navigate to another page on the site to be automatically logged inPlease refresh your browser to be logged in\", \"from\": 4992, \"to\": 5287, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5108, \"end\": 5119, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.0119096630085941e-16, \"text\": \"Independent\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Independent\"}]}]}"